title: #114: Cryptids With The Boogie Monster's Kyle Kinane and David Stone
description: Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  This episode we discuss the wonderful world of Cryptids with the guys from The Boogie Monster podcast, Kyle Kinane and David Stone! Thanks for tuning in. We appreciate your support!
